                <h1>Rehire Background Check Policy: Ensure Safe Hiring</h1>
                <p>A rehire background check policy ensures a thorough examination of former employees seeking to return, safeguarding the company's integrity. This policy covers criminal records, employment verification, and any previous disciplinary actions. By implementing this policy, organizations can make informed hiring decisions and maintain a safe workplace.</p>
